  <name>Wally</name>
  <summary>Manage wallpaper slideshows for Day and Night themes</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Wally is a GNOME desktop application that helps you manage wallpaper slideshows
      with automatic day and night theme switching. Select folders containing your
      favorite wallpapers for light and dark themes, configure slideshow timing,
      and let Wally automatically switch between them based on your system theme.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Separate wallpaper collections for day and night themes</li>
      <li>Automatic theme-based wallpaper switching</li>
      <li>Configurable slideshow intervals (1 minute to 1 hour)</li>
      <li>Smooth fade transitions between wallpapers</li>
      <li>Manual wallpaper skipping</li>
      <li>GNOME HIG compliant interface using libadwaita</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
